lomse README file
Version: v0.0
Last update: 2010-09-19
-----------------------

LenMus open music score edition library (Lomse library) for C++ is a free open source library to add capabilities to any program for editing, rendering and playing back music scores. It is witten in C++ and it is platform independent, and developed using TDD (Test Driven Development) .
Lomse is based on the experience gained developping the LenMus project (www.lenmus.org) and it is, currently a work in progress.

Lomse is free software distributed under the terms of the GNU General Public License version 3 or later.

website:   http://lomse.sourceforge.net/
email: cecilios@users.sourceforge.net

